---
description: Suggest Cursor hooks when repeated validation commands indicate automation opportunities.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Suggest a hook only after a real repeated pattern (same check requested 2+ times).
- Keep hook suggestions contextual and brief.
- Prioritize fast hooks that do not noticeably slow iteration.
- Merge into existing `.cursor/hooks.json` instead of overwriting it.
- Prefer non-blocking script behavior unless explicitly requested otherwise.
